# Optional. Astryx does NOT need an API key to run — all body positions come
# from the keyless JPL Horizons API. This is kept only for a possible future
# feature (e.g. an APOD photo skybox), and is not read by the game today.
#
# To use one: grab a free key at https://api.nasa.gov/, copy this file to
# `.env`, and fill it in. `.env` is gitignored so your key never gets committed.
NASA_API_KEY=your_key_here
